display types

1 - Displayed both in Detail view and Edit view
2 - Displayed only in the Detail view (Ex. Created time, Modified time)
3 - It is not displayed both in DetailView and EditView,but can be shown in ListView
Example: Total, subtotal in Invoice Module. These Fields are not tied to any block.
4 - Added for handling passwords.


presence

0 - A sort of "system" field. One that should always be visible.
1 - A Hidden/Inactive field
2 - A "normal-use" field
